- Evaluate if allocating memory from the Python heap reduces performance

- What about the mallocs libuv does on its own?

- Implement stop / close functions in watchers, instead of 'destroy'

- UDP client support

- FS module with all filesystem related functions from libuv

- Review Python reference counting in cases where errors are produced

- Add support for named pipes

- Add support for spawning child processes

